ocale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link> of the principal Act</citation> is consequentially amended by omitting the expression <amend.in><citation jurisdiction="nz">section 11G(6)</citation></amend.in>, and substituting the expression <amend.in><citation jurisdiction="nz">section 11J</citation></amend.in>.</text>
            </para>
          </subprov>
          <subprov skeleton="no" xml:lang="en-NZ">
